ary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/BitOperations.cs#L97'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/System.Numerics.BitOperations.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Performs a left bitwise rotation on a 32-bit unsigned integer.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static uint RotateLeft(uint value, int offset)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>value</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.uint32'>uint</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/System.Numerics.BitOperations.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The value to rotate.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>offset</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int32'>int</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/System.Numerics.BitOperations.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The number of bits to rotate by.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.uint32'>uint</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/System.Numerics.BitOperations.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The result of rotating <code class=\"paramref\">value</code> left by <code class=\"paramref\">offset</code> bits.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='System.Numerics.BitOperations.RoundUpToPowerOf2(System.UInt32)' data-commentId='M:System.Numerics.BitOperations.RoundUpToPowerOf2(System.UInt32)' id='System_Numerics_BitOperations_RoundUpToPowerOf2_System_UInt32_'>RoundUpToPowerOf2(uint)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/BitOperations.cs#L81'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/System.Numerics.BitOperations.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">rounds up to the next highest power of 2.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static uint RoundUpToPowerOf2(uint value)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>value</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.uint32'>uint</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.uint32'>uint</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
